          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Silverline has always been a popular choice for parents who want their child to develop into a well rounded confident individual. I highly recommend this school to everyone. In this day and age of showing off big infrastructure and buildings to lure parents, Silverline is one of those schools that has always stood for quality education, good values and overall personality development of the child. Under the able guidance of Dr. Mala Kapoor, children has been exposed to so many activities and have been given amazing platforms. No child is ever discouraged, the teachers like to find out the unique capability of the child and work towards enhancing it. that's what I have always appreciated about Silverline.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
