          },
          "datePublished": "2023-03-24",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My Son today completed his first happy year in this highly recommended school with lots of learning and overall growth as a child. We were skeptical in the beginning because of past experience in the play school and he just did not want to go to school. However the very first interaction with Mala mam was very positive and the experience just got better with his teacher Supriya mam as our son loves going to school and learn with fun. Thanks to all the teachers & staff of the school for their hard work and building a positive environment for learning & development.",
